<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> matirai koṇṭa kopparakecaripaṟmakku yāṇṭu <num value="32">3 <g type="numeral">10</g> 2</num>
<lb n="2"/>Āvatu Ivvāṇ ṭumpaḷa nāṭṭup peruntevatāṉan tirumaṟaikkā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṭṭu <hi rend="grantha">ma</hi>h<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ā</corr></choice>tevarkku Aḷanāṭṭukkiḻaiyil Iruntu vāḻum veḷḷā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭṭi cāttaṉ malli vacca nontāviḷakku 1 Oṉṟiṉukku vacca Āṭu toṇ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṇūṟuṅ koṇṭu tirumaṟaikkāṭaṉāl nicatam Uḻakkup paṭi ney cantirātitta
<lb n="6" break="no"/>val muṭṭāmey Aṭṭuvomāṉom tirumaṟaikkāṭṭut tevariṭaiccāṉṟom
<lb n="7"/>Itu <hi rend="grantha">panmāheśvara rakṣai <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi>
</p>

